  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Architectural Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>ARCHITECTECTURAL COORDINATOR</strong></p>\n<p>(Building Construction/Project)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To assist PM/PE to plan &amp; execute structural &amp; architectural works</li>\n  <li>Lead in site coordination with all trades</li>\n  <li>To liaise with RTO for inspection</li>\n  <li>Prepare; submission of shop drawings/Materials/MOS</li>\n  <li>To check shop drawings submitted by Sub-contractors</li>\n  <li>To ensure work is construct in accordance with contract and drawings</li>\n  <li>Liaise with sub contractors, suppliers etc</li>\n  <li>Procurement and monitoring of Architectural related materials</li>\n  <li>To carry out inspection/trade demo/material testing/mock-up</li>\n  <li>To check and ensure compliance with TOP check list and RI (Achi)</li>\n  <li>Attend subcon meetings</li>\n  <li>Contract administration and other site operational &amp; project management matters</li>\n  <li>Any other works as assigned by the Management or your Superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree of Architecture or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant work experience in building/construction trade in Singapore such as in D&amp;B project (government/commercial building) or HDB BTO project</li>\n  <li>Preferred Singaporean to apply</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
